title: Large Main Floor Duplex for 10/1, Sun Room, Full Dining Room, Garage
posting_body: ['Large & Bright Main Floor Duplex Available October 1 in Mac Groveland, Full Dining Room, Sun Room, Garage Included', 'Property Address', '1892 Lincoln Ave - Lower Unit | St. Paul, MN 55105', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'Guardian Property Management |', 'show contact info', 'Description', 'With occupied units, we are only able to do a showing after an application is approved.', ' To apply, each adult would fill out an application at <URL> and upload last two pay statements and proof of other income.', 'RENT SPECIAL!', ' - Rent will be reduced to $1500/month for a 2 year lease.', 'Main floor unit in duplex available October 1 in Mac Groveland.', 'Large living room is open to the dining room.', "There's a lot of natural light and built-ins along the entire wall of the dining room.", "There's a sun room off the living room that's perfect for an office or all of your house plants.", ' Original woodwork throughout with crown mouldings.', 'Both bedrooms have hardwood floors and ceiling fans.', 'The master bedroom has a cedar lined closet with additional storage behind it.', " There's a full bathroom between the bedrooms with tiled shower and pedestal sink.", 'The kitchen has all appliances including a dishwasher and microwave.', 'Beautiful shared back yard and one stall in the garage is included.', "There's additional storage and laundry in the basement.", "Great location in St. Paul's Mac Groveland neighborhood.", 'One cat or small dog under 35lbs is okay with $50/month pet fee', 'Rent includes water, trash, lawn care and snow removal', '$50 application fee per adult', 'We check income (gross household income must be at least 3 times rent), credit (must be 600+), criminal and rental history', 'Call Dakota at', 'show contact info', 'for more information', 'Agent: Dakota DeHaven', 'BROKER: GUARDIAN PROPERTY MANAGEMENT AND SERVICES LLC', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 1,183', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,550.00', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $50.00', 'Security Deposit: $1,550.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Small dogs allowed']
